Class NfsDirectoryEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.emc.ecs.nfsclient.nfs.NfsDirectoryEntry
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    NfsDirectoryPlusEntry

    public class NfsDirectoryEntry
extends java.lang.Object
    Holder for entries returned by READDIR calls, as specified by RFC 1813 (https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc1813).
